    <briefdescription>
<para>Transformation utilities for cameras, models, and scene graph inheritance. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>This module provides transformation functions and utilities including:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>**Camera transforms**: View matrix construction (`lookAt`)</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>**Model transforms**: Rotation, scaling, translation utilities</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>**TransformType**: Bitmask enum for selective transform inheritance</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para><simplesect kind="note"><para>Matrix operations `decompose()` and `transpose()` are available as member functions of `mat4` in `helios.math.types`. </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
